V \in C^2(\mathbb{R}^n,\mathbb{R})
x_0 \in \mathbb{R}^n
n \ge 2
\phi_{x_0}: (t^-,t^+) \to \mathbb{R}^n
 \dot{x}=-\nabla V(x),\quad x(0)=x_0. 
\phi_{x_0}(0)=\phi_{x_0}(p)
\phi_{x_0}
