     V(\phi_{x_0}(t))=V(\phi_{x_0}(0))
<\text{grad}V(\phi_{x_0}(t),\phi_{x_0}'(t)>=0\implies <-\phi_{x_0}'(t),\phi'_{x_0}(t)>=0
